{"tid":1529840,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[p牌都要轉載]勇武一日唔轉守為攻，一日都停止唔到送頭","createTime":"2019-09-01T22:46:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T22:55:06.000Z","uid":309846,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a9f434fdc83d4b0d83c06e8f4bab034ccb8d3853","tid":1529840,"uid":309846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T22:46:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4eXkZsA7vJE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4eXkZsA7vJE&d=c1rUz8TxCzzDRK4zYpKqdPaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=886776e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4eXkZsA7vJE</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n先睇下魚蛋呢條片<br />\n<br />\n當年冇Gear，人數同而家完全冇得比<br />\n<br />\n對方同樣被逼到向天開實彈，只係差冇出tear gas<br />\n<br />\n佢地係打到為數唔少既夠失去活動能力<br />\n<br />\n每令一隻狗無法行動，就可能令數以十計既手足免於被捕，此其一<br />\n<br />\n第二，點解當年做到？<br />\n<br />\n分別在於唔比任何時間差佬擺陣<br />\n<br />\n一見有狗車就衝上去，打到佢地車都落唔到，更莫講擺陣<br />\n<br />\n完全唔需要路障，魚蛋手足先係推進既一方<br />\n<br />\n當兩邊都冇陣式既時候，人數先發揮到作用<br />\n<br />\n當人地擺好陣，要破就唔係咁易，除非你揸架車衝入狗群<br />\n<br />\nBe water，破唔到陣，就令個陣出唔到世<br />\n<br />\n黃大仙first win嗰晚亦係同樣，入巴士站圍狗圍車，冇陣既狗只能敗走<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">總結：<br />\n<br />\n「狗車黎緊，快d起路障」= 送頭<br />\n<br />\n「狗車黎緊，快d過去打到佢車都唔敢落」= 魚蛋戰術</span></span>"},{"pid":"72ec9bc0afc1f8610b73a28c2ae47c4b5f5f14f2","tid":1529840,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T22:48:52.000Z","msg":"推！有冇post"},{"pid":"3106d75d7f8de9ab8827a5bf8e23e0ec69447a2c","tid":1529840,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T22:49:05.000Z","msg":"有用post"},{"pid":"84283d1cd490899e978727efa33a625c7244d4bb","tid":1529840,"uid":260695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T22:51:40.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"a198aa49e473bb6a28e8ede773d8297aa1c11006","tid":1529840,"uid":260814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T22:55:06.000Z","msg":"推！魚蛋戰術！"}]}